---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout>


    <main style="background-color: #FAF3E3;" class="" >
        <div class="p-4 container mx-auto">
            <h1 class="border-b text-5xl font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <h3 class=" mt-3 text-xl font-bold">
                Privacy Policy
            </h3>
            <h3 class=" my-3 text-xl font-bold">
                Last updated: February 10, 2026
            </h3>
            <p class=" border-b">
                Welcome to Mailan Home Bakery. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how
                information
                may be
                collected and used when you visit mailanhomebakery.com.
            </p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold my-3">
                Information We Collect
            </h3>
            <p class="border-b">
                We do <b>not</b> intentionally or manually collect personal information from visitors.

                However, when you visit our website, certain information may be collected automatically by our hosting
                provider <b>(Render)</b>
                and third-party services, including but not limited to:
            <ul class="list-disc ms-3">
                <li>
                    IP address
                </li>

                <li>
                    Browser type

                </li>
                <li>

                    Pages visited
                </li>
                <li>
                    Date and time of access

                </li>

            </ul>


            This information is used for basic website functionality, security, and performance monitoring.

            </p>

            <h3 class="my-3 text-xl font-bold">
                Cookies
            </h3>

            <p class="border-b">
                We do not use cookies for personal tracking purposes.
                However, third-party services integrated into the site (such as advertising or analytics providers) may
                use
                cookies or similar technologies to serve content and ads.

                You can disable cookies through your browser settings if you prefer.
            </p>

            <h3 class="my-3 text-xl font-bold">
                Google AdSense
            </h3>

            <p class="border-b">
                We may display advertisements served by <b>Google AdSense</b>.

                Google uses cookies (including the DoubleClick cookie) to show ads based on users’ visits to this and
                other
                websites. This allows the display of ads that are relevant to users.

                You can opt out of personalized advertising by visiting Google Ads Settings.
            </p>

            <h3 class="my-3 text-xl font-bold">
                Google Analytics
            </h3>
            <p class="border-b">
                We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors engage with our site. Google Analytics collects data
                such as your IP address, browser type, device information, pages visited, and time spent on the site.
                To learn more, visit
                <a target="_blank" href="https://policies.google.com/privacy">
                    Google’s Privacy Policy.
                </a>
            </p>

            <h3 class="my-3 text-xl font-bold">
                Third-Party Services
            </h3>

            <p class="border-b">
                Our Privacy Policy does not apply to other websites or services that may be linked to or integrated with
                our
                site. We encourage users to review the Privacy Policies of any third-party services they interact with.
            </p>

            <h3 class="my-3 text-xl font-bold">
                Children’s Information

            </h3>

            <p class="border-b">
                Mailan Home Bakery does not knowingly collect any Personal Identifiable Information from children under
                the age
                of 13. If you believe your child has provided personal information on our website, please contact us and
                we will
                promptly remove it.
            </p>

            <h3 class="my-3 text-xl font-bold">
                Consent
            </h3>

            <p class="border-b">
                By using our website, you consent to this Privacy Policy and agree to its terms.
            </p>

            <h3 class="my-3 text-xl font-bold">
                Contact Us

            </h3>

            <p class="border-b">

                If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you may contact us at:

                <a href="mailto:mailanplannerco@gmail.com">
                    📧mailanplannerco@gmail.com
                </a>
            </p>




        </div>


    </main>

</Layout>
